  "description": "<p>\n\tThe vowel /ɒ/ is a <span style=\"color: #f00;\">lot </span><span style=\"color: #f00;\">softer </span>than its <span style=\"color: #f00;\">strong and long <span style=\"color: #000;\">counterpart.</span><br />\n\t</span>元音/ɒ/与它相应的长元音/ɔ:/相比，肌肉放松得多。</p>\n<p>\n\t【发音要领】</p>\n<p>\n\t/ɒ/是一个短元音，发音时嘴唇和舌头都比发长元音/ɔ:/时要放松，具体表现在：舌尖位置不变，但舌中部下沉及舌根向后上方推送的幅度都比/ɔ:/要小；嘴唇稍向前突出，幅度小于长元音/ɔ:/，因而双颌打开的幅度也略大；相对于<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784832/\" target=\"_blank\">/ɔ:/在口腔中形成的椭圆柱形通道</a>，它的感觉更象一个乒乓球。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/48c2eead20ad42faaa938c9febe6c2cb.jpg\" style=\"height: 299px; width: 300px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t【看视频学语音】<br />\n\t首先奉上英国语音学教授Alex的教学视频涨涨姿势：</p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t再来一段萌萌的卡通片段减减龄：</p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t【常见字母组合】</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784833\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\to&mdash;fond, pond, stop, dot；<br />\n\ta&mdash;want, was, wander, wash</p>\n<p>\n\t【发音练习】</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784833\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t1. All I want is a proper cup of coffee made in a proper copper coffee pot.<br />\n\t2.&nbsp;Dog often hopped off the hot rock and crossed the common to watch the swans, because he wanted to scoff the lot.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本文系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784833/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784833\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p789945/\">卡梅伦辞职演讲双语全文 附语言点精析</a></li><li style